column5: I am looking for info on a couple ouposts in Ear Falls. Wenasaga outposts run Jubilee Lake outpost and Slate Lake outpost. Also any info on Latreille Lake lodge. The have Allison and Margaret lake outpost. If anyone has fished these outposts can you let me know how your trip was? How was fishing, boats, motors, cabins etc. Any info would be greatly appreciated!!!
